Content-Transfer-Encoding: 7bit
Content-Disposition: inline

Why is there no modulus function in Axiom?&nbsp; Such as<br><br>-13 mod 10 producing 7.<br><br>There&#39;s rem, but if you want a positive value you have to tweak the result.&nbsp; I can get x mod n with (x::ZMOD n)::INT but that&#39;s a bit of a kludge, and if I put it in a program the compiler doesn&#39;t like it.
<br><br>Thanks,<br>Alasdair<br>

